title: TVS Motor unveils TVS Apache RTR 160 4V with dual channel ABS at Rs 1.34 lakh
description: The bike was launched at the third edition of TVS Motosoul - the flagship motorcycle festival by TVS Motor in Goa. The occasion also marked the extension of TVS Motor and Petronas' collaboration for the next season. "The focus of the partnership will also be on introducing co-branded merchandise that aligns with the values and identity of both the brands.", a company statement said.
